7 An Act relating to professions and occupations;
7 amending 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1253, as amended by
8 Section 1, Chapter 65, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp.
8 2024, Section 1253), which relates to the State Board
9 of Licensed Social Workers; extending sunset date;
9 providing an effective date; and declaring an
10 emergency.
10
