13 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13
14 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 59 O.S. 2021, Section 1253, as
14
15 amended by Section 1, Chapter 65, O.S.L. 2023 (59 O.S. Supp. 2024,
15
16 Section 1253), is amended to read as follows:
16
17 Section 1253. A. There is hereby re-created, to continue until
17
18 July 1, 2025 July 1, 2026, in accordance with the provisions of the
18
19 Oklahoma Sunset Law, the State Board of Licensed Social Workers,
19
20 consisting of seven (7) members.
20
21 B. Three of the members of the Board shall be licensed social
21
22 workers or licensed clinical social workers licensed pursuant to the
22
23 provisions of the Social Worker’s Licensing Act. Two members shall
23
24 be licensed as either social work associates or master’s social
24
